{"tid":2168702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球新型肺炎逾2千2百萬　世衛：兩年內可結束疫情","createTime":"2020-08-22T03:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T11:14:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"54c061934a73d16dd09c323e9f983612f84a0637","tid":2168702,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"全球新型肺炎個案2千2百萬宗，累計79萬人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織認為，新型冠狀病毒引發的疫症大流行，可於兩年內結束。<br />\n<br />\n不過，譚德塞強調，前提是抗疫過程中，能實現國家和國際層面的團結協作，充分利用疫苗在內的應對措施。他重申，有效疫苗正式推出前，任何國家無法安然，迅速發現，預防集體感染及防止社區傳播，非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n另外，新加坡由9月起放寬對文萊及新西蘭旅客的限制，入境後無須隔離14天。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545237-20200822.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545237-20200822.htm&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThlm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=d540e737\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545237-20200822.htm&h=e41abac2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545237-20200822.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9dc217a50c580734a32615e2f66f78189dfd3f3c","tid":2168702,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T03:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff72483b999fe830ee36e213e7947c103604180","tid":2168702,"uid":6213,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T03:10:37.000Z","msg":"條柒頭皮幾時收皮"},{"pid":"a5a3901165cefd551d5461054c5bfe6d8cc2a55e","tid":2168702,"uid":137725,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T03:15:39.000Z","msg":"Thanks wor"},{"pid":"a43a7a3a55d0e71921126b72079f8c4cb6b6fdd3","tid":2168702,"uid":18477,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T03:17:07.000Z","msg":"能實現國家和國際層面的團結協作<br />\n<br />\n台灣同文明世界"},{"pid":"acbf3397fdb99df38ae28f